dream after his initiatives...

9
00:01:36.830 --> 00:01:39.540
... of making Goa
safe are falling flat.

10
00:05:04.620 --> 00:05:10.580
Take it. Pass the ball. Come on.

11
00:05:17.750 --> 00:05:19.200
Pass it!

12
00:06:10.250 --> 00:06:12.000
Hi. Roy.
- Hey. Max.

13
00:06:12.750 --> 00:06:14.910
Stop guzzling your beer factory.

14
00:06:15.290 --> 00:06:17.250
Or the pole won't hit the hole.

15
00:06:22.290 --> 00:06:23.410
Hello. boss.

16
00:06:25.660 --> 00:06:26.750
Roy.

17
00:06:39.700 --> 00:06:40.950
It's good.

18
00:06:43.200 --> 00:06:45.870
For the next few days and nights.
keep your...

19
00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.950
... eyes and ears wide open.

20
00:06:48.160 --> 00:06:49.080
Yes. boss.

21
00:06:49.620 --> 00:06:53.040
Nothing should move
in Goa without my knowledge.

22
00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:53.950
Do you understand?

23
00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.700
Absolutely. boss.

24
00:06:56.250 --> 00:06:57.450
Francis.

25
00:07:16.540 --> 00:07:17.910
Out of my way. Roy.

26
00:07:20.700 --> 00:07:21.620
Enough?

27
00:07:22.410 --> 00:07:23.580
Little more.

28
00:07:25.160 --> 00:07:26.080
Enough?

29
00:07:26.200 --> 00:07:27.290
Little bit more.

30
00:07:29.580 --> 00:07:30.910
That's better.

31
00:08:24.830 --> 00:08:27.370
Sir. Sir.

32
00:08:27.450 --> 00:08:29.620
Sir. we need your
statement on this case.

33
00:08:44.330 --> 00:08:45.330
Sir.

34
00:08:46.910 --> 00:08:48.250
Welcome back. sir.

35
00:09:02.660 --> 00:09:03.950
It's a cut-and-dry case. sir.

36
00:09:06.540 --> 00:09:07.950
I think it is...

37
00:09:08.870 --> 00:09:11.000
... a 'passion of crime' case.

38
00:09:12.160 --> 00:09:14.910
You know how these
foreigners are. sir.

39
00:09:15.700 --> 00:09:18.370
They just sleep around and...

40
00:09:22.790 --> 00:09:24.750
No. sir. It's not a forced entry.

41
00:09:25.870 --> 00:09:27.950
You know what I think happened?

42
00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:31.040
This Valery must be sitting with
someone in the bedroom.

43
00:09:33.330 --> 00:09:35.000
And Boris must have shown up.
all of a sudden.

44
00:09:35.910 --> 00:09:39.000
Seeing a third person in the house led
to a fight between Boris and Valery.

45
00:09:39.950 --> 00:09:42.540
While arguing. they must have
come from the bedroom to the hall.

46
00:09:42.620 --> 00:09:46.000
In his rage. Boris must have
raised his gun and fired at the boy.

47
00:09:46.120 --> 00:09:47.370
then Valery came in the way

48
00:09:47.450 --> 00:09:48.410
and Valery was shot dead!

49
00:09:49.700 --> 00:09:53.330
From the shock.
the gun slipped from Boris' hand.

50
00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:55.750
And that boy would have quickly

51
00:09:55.830 --> 00:09:57.870
grabbed the gun and aimed it at Boris.

52
00:09:59.040 --> 00:10:01.000
Boris must've been terrified!

53
00:10:02.290 --> 00:10:05.200
He must have begged
for his life sitting on the sofa.

54
00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:08.000
But no. the boy didn't
listen to his pleas!

55
00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:10.000
Just aimed at his head.

56
00:10:10.040 --> 00:10:13.040
And bang. bang. bang!
Boris is done too!

57
00:10:14.040 --> 00:10:16.000
It's an open-and-shut case. sir.

58
00:10:18.200 --> 00:10:19.450
Sit.

59
00:10:19.580 --> 00:10:20.750
Sir.

60
00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:44.250
What's the name you mentioned?
- Boris and Valery.

61
00:10:44.330 --> 00:10:46.200
Ghone
- Sorry. sir.

62
00:10:46.290 --> 00:10:47.160
Give me your hand.

63
00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:50.040
Your hand.

64
00:10:57.370 --> 00:11:00.790
People don't chop each other's thumbs
off in a crime of passion. Ghone.

65
00:11:34.450 --> 00:11:35.450
Who shot them?

66
00:11:36.200 --> 00:11:37.040
Who. boss?

67
00:11:39.540 --> 00:11:40.410
Who shot them?

68
00:11:40.580 --> 00:11:42.290
Boss. I don't know. I swear. boss.

69
00:11:42.370 --> 00:11:46.040
M***********r.
Constantly saying 'I don't know'!

70
00:11:46.580 --> 00:11:48.120
Isn't it your f*****g job to know?

71
00:11:48.370 --> 00:11:49.000
Isn't it?

72
00:11:49.410 --> 00:11:50.540
Yes. boss.

73
00:11:50.620 --> 00:11:51.790
Is it the f*****g blacks?

74
00:11:52.330 --> 00:11:54.660
- No. they couldn't.
- Those Kashmiri f*****s?

75
00:11:55.160 --> 00:11:56.950
No. they just met them there.

76
00:11:58.450 --> 00:12:00.620
You better find
out really quickly. Yeah?

77
00:12:00.700 --> 00:12:00.950
Yeah.

78
00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:03.000
Because the next time.
they catch you.

79
00:12:03.790 --> 00:12:05.250
it will be your f*****g d**k.

80
00:12:05.700 --> 00:12:07.000
they'll chop off for a change.

81
00:12:07.250 --> 00:12:08.040
You get that?

82
00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:10.330
F**k.

83
00:12:11.910 --> 00:12:13.040
Yes. Bhau.

84
00:12:13.700 --> 00:12:15.750
It's 100% Duman gang's job.

85
00:12:16.250 --> 00:12:19.040
If we don't retaliate.
they'll consider us eunuchs.

86
00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:21.000
They started this.

87
00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:22.410
Now. we'll end it.

88
00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:26.200
Let's go. everyone.

89
00:12:26.660 --> 00:12:27.700
Balu. start the car.

90
00:12:28.200 --> 00:12:28.950
Come fast.

91
00:12:29.330 --> 00:12:30.250
Hurry up.

92
00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:21.000
Bhau!

93
00:13:31.700 --> 00:13:32.700
I received this...

94
00:13:33.410 --> 00:13:34.580
... in the morning.

95
00:13:38.830 --> 00:13:39.410
I know.

96
00:13:40.450 --> 00:13:43.250
I too have received something similar.

97
00:13:45.450 --> 00:13:49.830
Your box has Boris' chopped thumb.

98
00:13:49.910 --> 00:13:55.950
And my box has Valery's.

99
00:13:57.410 --> 00:13:59.250
This is a message from them.

100
00:13:59.620 --> 00:14:01.040
They need our attention.

101
00:14:01.120 --> 00:14:02.660
So I'll give them that!

102
00:14:03.040 --> 00:14:04.000
Attention!

103
00:14:04.910 --> 00:14:06.290
Bloody Duman.

104
00:14:13.750 --> 00:14:14.830
Vilas.

105
00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:24.790
This is the time to be smart.

106
00:14:27.200 --> 00:14:28.950
This is the time to...

107
00:14:30.950 --> 00:14:32.450
... shake hands.

108
00:14:33.410 --> 00:14:34.160
What?

109
00:14:35.790 --> 00:14:37.660
You want to shake hands...

110
00:14:38.080 --> 00:14:39.910
... with those who would
happily chop ours off?

111
00:14:43.700 --> 00:14:45.290
Times have changed. Vilas.

112
00:14:46.910 --> 00:14:48.250
Now. those days are gone.

113
00:14:49.910 --> 00:14:53.580
If we try to fight Duman

114
00:14:53.660 --> 00:14:56.370
in the streets.
the new CM will benefit.

115
00:15:00.580 --> 00:15:03.080
Under the scheme of Education For All.
the government...

116
00:15:03.160 --> 00:15:07.200
... gives mid-day
meals to millions of students...

117
00:15:07.370 --> 00:15:11.040
... in around 12.650 schools. daily.

118
00:15:11.370 --> 00:15:12.790
And the Supreme Court
has issued an order

119
00:15:12.870 --> 00:15:15.950
that every meal must
contain 300 calories.

120
00:15:16.000 --> 00:15:17.750
1 bowl of lentil...

121
00:15:19.040 --> 00:15:20.250
will have 200...

122
00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:26.330
1 bowl of watery lentil...

123
00:15:26.870 --> 00:15:29.910
... has 50 calories.

124
00:15:31.290 --> 00:15:33.080
Tell me the total now?

125
00:15:33.290 --> 00:15:34.620
How much is it?

126
00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:37.580
How many calories add up?

127
00:15:41.370 --> 00:15:42.370
What's this?

128
00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:46.000
Is this lentil. hmmm?

129
00:15:46.950 --> 00:15:48.370
This is what you
will feed the children?

130
00:15:53.580 --> 00:15:54.580
Eat it.

131
00:15:55.620 --> 00:15:56.830
Sir.

132
00:16:00.040 --> 00:16:01.290
Nonsense.

133
00:16:06.000 --> 00:16:12.370
If they will kill our men
and parcel us their chopped fingers...

134
00:16:13.200 --> 00:16:15.000
... we must repay in kind.

135
00:16:15.830 --> 00:16:19.830
I won't refute that.
but use your brain.

136
00:16:21.040 --> 00:16:22.290
Not brute force.

137
00:16:23.790 --> 00:16:27.580
Our hands are tied.

138
00:16:30.370 --> 00:16:37.080
All our damn political connections
are currently in the Opposition.

139
00:16:37.830 --> 00:16:42.290
This damned new government.
new CM and new people

140
00:16:42.370 --> 00:16:49.790
are waiting for
us to make a mistake...

141
00:16:52.450 --> 00:16:56.160
... so that they can jump on us.

142
00:16:57.750 --> 00:17:00.000
To break us.

143
00:17:01.410 --> 00:17:04.950
To break our business.

144
00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:08.540
Vilas?

145
00:17:10.870 --> 00:17:15.290
If. at this time.
we go about making enemies...

146
00:17:17.700 --> 00:17:19.910
... then we will be broken. my friend.

147
00:17:20.000 --> 00:17:23.160
And that is what this new CM wants.

148
00:17:24.120 --> 00:17:25.540
I have only one mission.

149
00:17:27.080 --> 00:17:28.750
Crime and drug-free Goa.

150
00:17:30.950 --> 00:17:32.790
Do whatever it takes
to make it happen.

151
00:17:33.160 --> 00:17:35.580
By next week.
you will receive your transfer orders.

152
00:17:35.660 --> 00:17:37.000
Narcotics. special branch.

153
00:17:37.620 --> 00:17:38.450
You will lead it.

154
00:17:38.910 --> 00:17:39.830
Sir.

155
00:17:39.950 --> 00:17:44.000
By the way. what's the update
on this double murder case?

156
00:17:46.750 --> 00:17:49.370
Sir. according to me.

157
00:17:50.410 --> 00:17:51.450
it's a statement.

158
00:17:51.580 --> 00:17:52.790
from one cartel to another.

159
00:17:56.910 --> 00:18:01.120
Pereira. next time we should
be the ones making a statement.

160
00:18:04.450 --> 00:18:05.250
Sir.

161
00:18:14.660 --> 00:18:17.830
The new CM thinks he's very smart.

162
00:18:20.660 --> 00:18:22.200
Vilas...

163
00:18:25.830 --> 00:18:28.000
We will buy our time. my friend.

164
00:18:28.120 --> 00:18:29.790
We will buy our time.

165
00:18:29.870 --> 00:18:31.950
And when our time comes.

166
00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:33.910
we will strike so hard and so fast

167
00:18:37.040 --> 00:18:39.870
that they won't know.
It will be check...

168
00:18:39.950 --> 00:18:43.120
... and mate.

169
00:18:44.040 --> 00:18:46.870
There's a benefit
in shaking hands with Duman.

170
00:18:48.330 --> 00:18:51.000
Our supply will double.

171
00:18:52.870 --> 00:18:55.750
Even after sharing the profit...

172
00:18:56.370 --> 00:18:59.660
... we will make much more money.
I think...

173
00:19:01.910 --> 00:19:03.410
... ten times more.

174
00:19:32.660 --> 00:19:33.580
Reddy sir.

175
00:19:37.830 --> 00:19:38.450
Full amount?

176
00:19:41.120 --> 00:19:42.000
Reddy sir.

177
00:19:44.120 --> 00:19:44.870
Yes.

178
00:19:47.370 --> 00:19:49.000
You own the entire port.

179
00:19:49.580 --> 00:19:50.700
But what do you get in return?

180
00:19:51.580 --> 00:19:54.700
Moshe Barak and Vilas
Satham get all the cream.

181
00:19:57.200 --> 00:19:59.290
You're needlessly getting scared.

182
00:20:00.580 --> 00:20:01.910
Nothing will happen.

183
00:20:05.790 --> 00:20:09.410
Be happy with whatever you get.

184
00:20:10.950 --> 00:20:12.620
You cater to tourists.

185
00:20:13.660 --> 00:20:15.000
Stay like one.

186
00:20:15.910 --> 00:20:18.830
You know my supply is of top quality.

187
00:20:25.000 --> 00:20:26.370
50-50.

188
00:20:54.580 --> 00:20:55.700
Get me some ice.

189
00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:57.000
Yes sir.

190
00:21:08.540 --> 00:21:09.790
Get me some ice!

191
00:21:14.950 --> 00:21:17.580
- Where's the ice. you moron?
- Pushya.

192
00:21:17.910 --> 00:21:18.580
Where's the ice?

193
00:21:18.660 --> 00:21:19.540
Give me the damn ice!

194
00:21:20.000 --> 00:21:21.000
Pushkar.

195
00:21:24.580 --> 00:21:25.660
Yes. Bhau. tell me.

196
00:21:26.040 --> 00:21:27.000
What's the problem?

197
00:21:28.870 --> 00:21:31.580
You're in a great mood today.

198
00:21:48.370 --> 00:21:52.000
They are hunting down
and killing our boys like dogs.

199
00:21:53.000 --> 00:21:54.540
And we intend to
shake hands with them?

200
00:21:55.660 --> 00:21:57.250
They should fear us.

201
00:21:57.580 --> 00:21:58.620
I can't understand anything.

202
00:21:58.700 --> 00:21:59.660
What's happening?

203
00:22:01.120 --> 00:22:04.750
I think. we should find
each of them and bury them alive.

204
00:22:07.000 --> 00:22:10.620
Sometimes one can exude
power by using the brain.

205
00:22:13.620 --> 00:22:15.040
Pretty sure Moshe said this. right?

206
00:22:15.410 --> 00:22:16.450
Definitely!

207
00:22:20.750 --> 00:22:24.910
All this is a game of supply. Pushya.

208
00:22:26.580 --> 00:22:31.450
You understand everything now.

209
00:22:34.830 --> 00:22:36.660
Moshe brings the supply.

210
00:22:37.580 --> 00:22:41.950
And only after the
supply is received. Pushya...

211
00:22:42.290 --> 00:22:45.000
... our power comes to use.

212
00:22:45.700 --> 00:22:48.000
Only after the supply is received.
Is that clear?

213
00:22:48.200 --> 00:22:50.290
Is Moshe a God. Bhau?

214
00:22:50.910 --> 00:22:55.330
If there's no supply.
what's the use of power?

215
00:22:55.410 --> 00:22:56.580
So what do we do now?

216
00:22:56.660 --> 00:22:58.450
Should we twiddle our thumbs?

217
00:23:01.370 --> 00:23:04.660
It takes two to tango.

218
00:23:07.000 --> 00:23:08.000
Ghone has told me that

219
00:23:09.620 --> 00:23:14.000
the CM has given full
powers to ACP Pereira.

220
00:23:15.330 --> 00:23:20.000
Now. Pereira will be
on our trail like a mad dog.

221
00:23:33.700 --> 00:23:35.000
So. what do we do Bhau?

222
00:23:37.620 --> 00:23:39.910
Today. we will receive a parcel.

223
00:23:41.040 --> 00:23:45.120
It's important to ensure that
it reaches the right place.

224
00:23:47.250 --> 00:23:48.200
Will be done. Bhau.

225
00:23:48.950 --> 00:23:50.290
Shall I say something. Bhau?

226
00:23:50.830 --> 00:23:52.370
This Duman.

227
00:23:52.620 --> 00:23:54.790
I can finish him in just one night.

228
00:23:54.870 --> 00:23:56.950
Just one night.

229
00:23:57.000 --> 00:23:58.250
You just say the word.

230
00:24:00.250 --> 00:24:02.910
When the time is right...

231
00:24:04.540 --> 00:24:05.830
... I will tell you.

232
00:24:13.410 --> 00:24:14.370
Cheers.

233
00:25:27.410 --> 00:25:28.120
Hello.

234
00:25:29.040 --> 00:25:30.660
Who's singing in the background?

235
00:25:31.370 --> 00:25:32.620
It's nothing. You tell me.

236
00:25:33.620 --> 00:25:35.950
There's an important delivery
to be picked from the godown.

237
00:25:36.330 --> 00:25:37.000
Understood?

238
00:25:37.620 --> 00:25:38.450
Consider it done.

239
00:25:39.000 --> 00:25:41.120
I'll call up Reddy. You get there now.

240
00:25:41.830 --> 00:25:42.910
I will see you at midnight.

241
00:25:43.620 --> 00:25:45.200
Don't worry. boss. I will manage.

242
00:25:45.830 --> 00:25:46.870
Shut up. f****r.

243
00:25:46.950 --> 00:25:48.540
I don't want overconfidence.

244
00:25:48.830 --> 00:25:50.790
It's more precious than your life.
understand?

245
00:25:51.450 --> 00:25:52.620
Be careful.

246
00:25:53.250 --> 00:25:55.000
Call me up if you need any help.

247
00:26:04.870 --> 00:26:06.040
R****l.

248
00:26:30.580 --> 00:26:32.870
Hey. what happened?

249
00:26:33.250 --> 00:26:35.040
Danny will be coming
at 4 AM to take the delivery.

250
00:26:35.120 --> 00:26:36.700
Pushkar sir had called twice.

251
00:26:42.000 --> 00:26:45.290
Hey. settle these
workers' payment. Come on.

252
00:27:32.700 --> 00:27:33.330
Hey. Chetta.

253
00:27:34.910 --> 00:27:35.700
You go.

254
00:27:39.250 --> 00:27:40.000
Good night.

255
00:28:05.790 --> 00:28:06.580
Hello. Kashmiri.

256
00:28:07.620 --> 00:28:10.000
You had offered me
a deal for 50-50. right?

257
00:28:10.700 --> 00:28:11.370
An opportunity's here.

258
00:28:12.870 --> 00:28:13.910
Meet me at Mapusa bridge.

259
00:28:15.120 --> 00:28:15.910
In half an hour.

260
00:28:16.910 --> 00:28:19.120
And. yes. Come alone.

261
00:30:29.830 --> 00:30:31.200
Hi Danny.

262
00:31:45.000 --> 00:31:46.660
There's a saying in Kashmiri language.

263
00:32:33.040 --> 00:32:34.160
F**k.

264
00:32:34.540 --> 00:32:35.540
F**k.

265
00:32:36.120 --> 00:32:37.250
F**k.

266
00:32:41.290 --> 00:32:42.160
F**k.

267
00:33:04.330 --> 00:33:05.660
Yes. tell me.

268
00:37:10.000 --> 00:37:10.040
Beep.

